<div class="landing-container">

  <!-- Seção 1: Hero / Destaque -->
  <header class="hero-section">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1>Contèm Cafés Especiais</h1>
      <p>Café de verdade, torrado sob demanda. Experimente o frescor máximo em cada xícara.</p>

      <% if user_signed_in? %>
        <%= link_to "Acessar Sistema", "#", class: "btn-primary" %>
      <% else %>
        <%= link_to "Eu quero", try_form_path, class: "btn-primary" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-image-wrapper">
      <%= image_tag "andre_coelho_red.png", class: "hero-img", alt: "Arte Contem Café" %>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Seção 2: Flyer e Conceito -->
  <section class="flyer-section">
    <div class="flyer-content">
      <h2>Experimente primeiro, pague o quanto achar justo</h2>
      <p>Acreditamos tanto na qualidade do nosso café recém-torrado que a experiência vem primeiro. Peça, prove e só depois pague o valor que sentir que valeu.</p>
      <p>Confira os detalhes da nossa sugestão de valor no flyer abaixo.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flyer-image-wrapper">
      <%= image_tag "flyer.png", class: "flyer-img", alt: "Flyer Contem Café - Pague o quanto achar justo" %>
    </div>
    <% if @payment_link.present? %>
      <div class="payment-copy-box">
        <button type="button" class="btn-copy-payment" data-copy-payment-link="<%= @payment_link %>">Copiar link de pagamento</button>
        <p class="payment-copy-feedback" aria-live="polite"></p>
      </div>
    <% end %>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <% unless user_signed_in? %>
        <%= link_to "Quero experimentar!", try_form_path, class: "btn-primary" %>
      <% end %>
      <%= link_to "Já provei!", satisfaction_survey_path, class: "btn-primary" %>
    </div>
  </section>

</div>

<style>
  /* CSS Básico Inline para a Landing Page */
  body {
    background-color: #fdfaf6; /* Um tom de branco café, para aconchego */
  }
  .landing-container {
    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
    color: #4a4a4a;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  /* Ocultar a Navbar apenas nesta página */
  .navbar, nav { display: none !important; }

  /* Hero Section */
  .hero-section {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 40px;
    padding: 4px 0 60px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .hero-text { flex: 1; min-width: 300px; }
  .hero-text h1 { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #2c3e50; line-height: 1.2; }
  .hero-text p { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 30px; }

  .hero-image-wrapper { flex: 1; min-width: 300px; position: relative; }
  .hero-img { width: 100%; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); object-fit: cover; }

  /* Flyer Section */
  .flyer-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 80px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
  .flyer-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .flyer-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .flyer-image-wrapper {
    margin: 40px 0;
  }

  .flyer-img {
    max-width: 800px;
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .payment-copy-box {
    margin: 0 auto 8px;
    max-width: 420px;
  }

  .btn-copy-payment {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 13px 18px;
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #8a1720;
    border: 1px solid #8a1720;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .btn-copy-payment:hover {
    background: #8a1720;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .payment-copy-feedback {
    display: none;
    margin: 8px 0 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #5c5c5c;
  }

  .payment-copy-feedback.is-visible {
    display: block;
  }

  .cta-row {
    margin-top: 10px;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 420px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .cta-row .btn-primary {
    flex: 0 0 calc((100% - 12px) / 2);
    box-sizing: border-box;
    min-width: 0;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 13px 18px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 15px 30px;
    background-color: #8a1720;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    transition: background-color 0.3s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background-color: #d35400;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .cta-row .btn-primary {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 420px;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  document.addEventListener("turbo:load", function() {
    var button = document.querySelector(".btn-copy-payment");
    var feedback = document.querySelector(".payment-copy-feedback");
    if (!button || !feedback) return;

    var link = button.dataset.copyPaymentLink;

    button.addEventListener("click", async function() {
      if (!link) return;

      try {
        if (navigator.clipboard && window.isSecureContext) {
          await navigator.clipboard.writeText(link);
        } else {
          var helperInput = document.createElement("textarea");
          helperInput.value = link;
          helperInput.setAttribute("readonly", "");
          helperInput.style.position = "absolute";
          helperInput.style.left = "-9999px";
          document.body.appendChild(helperInput);
          helperInput.select();
          document.execCommand("copy");
          document.body.removeChild(helperInput);
        }

        feedback.textContent = "Link copiado. Agora é so colar no navegador ou no app do banco.";
        feedback.classList.add("is-visible");
      } catch (error) {
        feedback.textContent = "Nao foi possivel copiar automaticamente. Pressione e segure para copiar manualmente.";
        feedback.classList.add("is-visible");
      }
    });
  });
</script>
